 *     B      B      II    N N     N   AAA        TTTT     AAA
 *     B      BB     II    N  N    N   AAAA        TT      AAAA
 *     BBBBBBBBB     II    N   N   N   AAAAA       TT      AAAAA
 *     B        BB   II    N   N   N   AA   A      TT      AA   A
 *     B        BB   II    N    N  N   AA    A     TT      AA    A
 *     BBBBBBBBBB   IIII   N    NNNN   AA     A   TTTT     AA     A
